{"tid":1159813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★畢業時間又到了！金融界CEO：IT人才難求","createTime":"2019-05-18T04:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T08:49:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"33e6acce1ba7c360ece54f6f4065d9477b1a0432","tid":1159813,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>金融界CEO：兼備美術、IT人才難求　盼應徵者懂溝通、願進修</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港大多家長重視子女成績，希望子女能考好公開試，成為專業人士，但多名出席「與傑出領袖對話」活動的CEO均表示，隨著科技發展快速，社會變化大，除了傳統專業人才，社會更需要不斷學習且能與人溝通的「通才」，例如是會編寫程式及了解商業服務的人才。而應徵者除了要有廣闊視野及認知，方便與不同人士溝通及接觸外，亦須有不斷學習的熱誠，以適應社會的發展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2810878/org/a7b8033cdafcf82ac8ee5f67109a7876.jpg/ro5XsiHkN5tSbiPP5pht3BbOz6yCNpU2hfUOEa_1DhE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2810878%2Forg%2Fa7b8033cdafcf82ac8ee5f67109a7876.jpg%2Fro5XsiHkN5tSbiPP5pht3BbOz6yCNpU2hfUOEa_1DhE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=45e6caa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/330276/金融界ceo-兼備美術-it人才難求-盼應徵者懂溝通-願進修\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F330276%2F%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E7%95%8Cceo-%E5%85%BC%E5%82%99%E7%BE%8E%E8%A1%93-it%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E9%9B%A3%E6%B1%82-%E7%9B%BC%E6%87%89%E5%BE%B5%E8%80%85%E6%87%82%E6%BA%9D%E9%80%9A-%E9%A1%98%E9%80%B2%E4%BF%AE&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkEPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=8686f05f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/330276/金融界ceo-兼備美術-it人才難求-盼應徵者懂溝通-願進修</a>"},{"pid":"48b46a6bd62de9332fffba7bbe9f3dc32e3b0920","tid":1159813,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rHi1PU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rHi1PU.png&h=0258f29c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88e8fda52091ea3b7b5e4e17fecf6a72db135842","tid":1159813,"uid":103759,"like":5,"disli